menu "TimeDisk UI Display"

    config UI_DISPLAY_INVERT
        bool "Invert display colors"
        default n
        help
            Invert all LCD colors via the panel driver. The Waveshare BSP enables
            invert during init; leave this disabled for normal colors.

    config UI_DISPLAY_ROTATE_180
        bool "Rotate display and touch 180 degrees"
        default y
        help
            Flip the entire UI upside down. Uses hardware panel mirroring for the
            LCD and LVGL's display rotation so touch coordinates stay aligned.

endmenu
